@base_url = http://localhost:5000/api

### 1. Register User (with Phone)
POST {{base_url}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "buyer_test",
  "email": "buyer@test.com",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!"
}

### 2. Get Landing Page Products
GET {{base_url}}/product/landing

### 3. Search Products
GET {{base_url}}/product?keyword=Product&pageSize=10

### 4. Search with Category Filter
GET {{base_url}}/product?categoryId=1

### 5. Get Categories Hierarchy
GET {{base_url}}/product/categories

### 6. Get Product Details (by ID)
GET {{base_url}}/product/1

### 7. Get Product Details (by Slug)
GET {{base_url}}/product/slug/product-21-9374

### 8. Add to Cart (Login required)
POST {{base_url}}/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 21,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 9. Get My Cart
GET {{base_url}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Create Address
POST {{base_url}}/address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Nguyen Van A",
  "phone": "0123456789",
  "street": "123 Le Loi",
  "city": "HCM",
  "country": "Vietnam",
  "isDefault": true
}

### 11. Get My Addresses
GET {{base_url}}/address
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Validate Coupon
POST {{base_url}}/coupon/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "orderAmount": 500000
}

### 13. Create Order
POST {{base_url}}/order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addressId": 1,
  "paymentMethod": "COD",
  "couponCode": "WELCOME10",
  "note": "Giao hàng giờ hành chính"
}

### 14. Get My Order History
GET {{base_url}}/order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Cancel Order
PUT {{base_url}}/order/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
